'''''Lordlings of Yore''''' is a 1983 video game published by [[Softlore Corporation]].

==Gameplay==
''Lordlings of Yore'' is a game in which the player is the lord of a shire who must manage knights and wealth, and eliminate opposing lords in a game involving strategy, tactics, and diplomacy.<ref name="CGW18"/>

==Reception==
''[[Computer Gaming World]]'' reviewed the game and stated that "The graphic presentation of the game is excellent and overall I found the game enjoyable. There are enough alternatives and actions in this game to continue to make it interesting to play over and over again."<ref name="CGW18">{{cite magazine |title=Micro-Reviews |magazine=Computer Gaming World |date=October 1984 |volume=1 |issue=18 |pages=38, 42}}</ref>

In a retrospective review of ''Lordlings of Yore'' in ''[[Black Gate (magazine)|Black Gate]]'', John ONeill said "''Lordlings of Yore'' had a lot of promise, but I can only conjecture it was an abysmal failure as a commercial release."<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.blackgate.com/2013/08/26/vintage-bits-lordlings-of-yore/|title = Vintage Bits: Lordlings of Yore – Black Gate| date=26 August 2013 }}</ref>

